S.FORM: Don Anielak sraral hya'ga sisyuw na NBA, wal malaxmisuq qaniy la. kawas tay 1930, ryax sa tay 1 nqu tay 11, Don Anielak, squliq na p'unro. (mhuqil sa kawas tay 1995) mtzyaw mrhuw na qyanux aring qutux sen qeru kbhul mzimal payat kawas(1954) tehok qutux sen qeru kbhul mzimal magal kawas(1955) Anielak mzyu mari sazing pspung ryax maki Moberly pqwasan biru.suruw lga,musa Southwest Missouri krahu pqwasan biru,hiya 1952 1954 kawas maki qasa mzyu mari. hiya ru Bradley msqun mzyu mari,1951 kawas pspung ryax,te qutux pspung mgyay la. 1953 kawas 1 byacing,Anielak magal 39 maki Missouri. 1989 kawas Southwest Missouri.tmwang pincyogan nya masoq krahu' pqwasan biru lga, Anielak te cyugal lahuy(26 ) tmwang New York Knicks maki 1954 kawas ru 1954 kawas 8 byacing mzyu mari hlahuy biru. .1954 kawas 11 byacing,hiya mhtuw Knicks magal cyugal . tman sgleng pincyogan masoq lga,Anielak ga sinsiy maki Charles na Peter's pqwasan biru,suruw lga,maki Ramsey Illinois cyugal pspung magal 56 18 ru musa Williamsville qeru pspung magal 134 55 1972 kawas,sinsiy pincyogan nya maki Missouri Koshkonong pqwasan biru. 1974 kawas musa Illinois na North Boone pqwasan biru.
